<a href=#L10000> Follow keywords </a><pre>
<a name=L10000></a><a href=#L10001>So</a>: U-af
From: woa0@emertel.gn.apc.org
Newsgroups: africa.news
Subject: Nigeria, Recent Documents, 2
Date: 29 May 1996 07:34:57

Path: gn!cdp!igc.apc.org!not-for-mail
From: woa@igc.apc.org
Newsgroups: africa.news
Subject: Nigeria, Recent Documents, 2
