http://www.knooppunt.be:80/~hit_run/caerts/adat.html 194.10.201.200 19970122041652 text/html 14087
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: CERN/3.0
Date: Wednesday, 22-Jan-97 05:16:52 GMT
