From: ecodefense@glas.apc.org
Newsgroups: reg.eeurope
Subject: ECODEFENSE!inform 85
Date: 23 May 1996 12:39:07 +0300

From: ecodefense@glas.apc.org (Vladimir Slivyak)

From ecodefense Thu May 23 12:35:58 1996
Received: by glas.apc.org
	via send-mail with stdio
	id  m0uMVsE-0003zKN@glas.apc.org 
	for ecodefense; Thu, 23 May 96 12:35:58 +0400 (GMT+0400)
	(Smail-3.1.92 1996-Mar-19 #5 built 1996-Apr-22)
Message-Id:  m0uMVsE-0003zKN@glas.apc.org 
Date: Thu, 23 May 96 12:35:58 +0400 (GMT+0400)
