PSKOV OBLAST- The construction of a coal-processing plant on the
territory of the Kalinin Kholkhoz, near the village of Zaguzy,
and also the construction of a temporary electrostation on
Iubileinii and Palkinskii Highways, have been temporarily
blocked. The reason for the halt in construction of both
projects is the absence of an ecological investigation in
project documentation. (Pskovskaia Pravda, 26 Dec.) 

