Traffic in Moscow

On December 23, Activists of "Rainbow Keepers" environmental
group were blocking some cars with cutted trees near Sadovoe
Koltso, center of the Moscow, where nobody can cut anything
green (tree or something else) by the act of Moscow government.
But worldwide known opera songer Ms. Vishnevskaya can cut this
trees to construct there opera schools (Moscow government,
forgetting first act, gave her the permission to cut by another
act). 4 activists were arrested, trial coming soon. Boycott
Vishnevskaya' opera concerts!

