RENEWABLE ENERGY TO ACCOUNT FOR 15%  OF PRIMARY ENERGY USED IN
THE EU BY THE YEAR  2010  -  COMMISSION  ANNOUNCES  AN  ACTION
PROGRAMME.
  
Unpaid Chernobyl  builders  on  hunger  strike,  KIEV,  July 5
(Reuter)  About  30  construction  workers  employed  in   the
"exclusion zone" around the Chernobyl nuclear power plant have
gone on hunger strike to press claims  for  months  of  unpaid
wages.

TASS July 8, 1996 HEADLINE: RUSSIAN ICEBREAKER CARRIES FOREIGN
