Subject: RADICAL VIDEO FOOTAGE WANTED!!!
Date: Tue, 30 Jul 1996 15:38:42 +0100 (BST)

From: train (Ted Oakes)

RADICAL VIDEO FOOTAGE WANTED!!!

I am looking for radical video footage from environmental and social
justice campaigns for possible use on our alternative video news magazine
and for a new BBC television series. This is a great opportunity to draw
attention to your group's activities and concerns.

Please send VHS copies of your material, explanatory information, contact
details or your questions to:

Ted Oakes
Undercurrents
16B Cherwell St.,
Oxford, OX4 1BG
England
Tel.  +44 1865 68750,  Fax +44 1865 243562
Train@gn.apc.org


