Subject: message 2, stop sea nuke transport!
Date: 02 Aug 1996 18:42:55 +0300

From: ecodefense@glas.apc.org (Vladimir Slivyak)

From ecodefense Fri Aug  2 18:37:56 1996
Received: by glas.apc.org
	via send-mail with stdio
	id  m0umLMR-00041jN@glas.apc.org 
	for ecodefense; Fri, 2 Aug 1996 18:37:55 +0400 (GMT+0400)
	(Smail-3.2 1996-Jul-4 #3 built 1996-Jul-13)
