form regularly.  The subscription is free. <a name=L10003></a><a href=#L10004>So</a> all the environ-
mentalists in the West or East can get this without any finan-
cial  problems.  This  is especially important for Third World
subscribers who can't pay even very  small  amount  of  money.
_______________________________________________________________
